note:
A typical desktop, laptop, or workstation, or even many servers, needs no more network configuration than
described already. Some additional network options, though, are useful on many computers. These include advanced
routing configurations and virtual private network (VPN) configurations. You should also be familiar with some
basic network-monitoring tool
